metadata.name: AGoldWorthyGully
metadata.description:
Stark radiance and the natural manipulation of man. 
Tangled labors of organic sensitivities. 
Awareness.
Energetic leaks and the captured embodiment of shadows.  
A celebrated marriage of flow & restraint. 


This is a the piece created in order to speak the inspirations of the natural art of Andy Goldsworthy. With great respect and admiration; Guy found a moment to share through the lens of emotional absorption and spectral reflection. 
A cerebral glimpse into the sight of this viewer.

Hard lines and blurred contrasts - like images burnt into forgotten sight. Dancing movements and cold stillness - each part representing the whole experience of witnessing Andy's masterful connection to the earthen orchestra of landscape.
